1691
01:46:56,135 --> 01:47:00,306
Anyway, 20
minutes of coming attractions.

1692
01:47:00,307 --> 01:47:02,703
All black films, all violent.

1693
01:47:02,704 --> 01:47:05,729
And I'm talking about
brothers shooting brothers.

1694
01:47:05,730 --> 01:47:10,212
I hate you going to the movies without me.
Oh, baby. Mm.

1695
01:47:10,213 --> 01:47:12,818
My pieces queen.
Oh, baby.

1696
01:47:12,819 --> 01:47:14,800
Mm.
Mm.

1697
01:47:14,801 --> 01:47:17,304
I hate seeing
movies without you.

1698
01:47:20,119 --> 01:47:22,726
I won't do it anymore. Okay?

1699
01:47:22,727 --> 01:47:25,229
Okay. Okay. I promise.

1700
01:47:27,732 --> 01:47:30,234
Another one. Mmm! Mmm!

1701
01:47:30,235 --> 01:47:32,320
Chi-chi-bear. Mm!

1702
01:47:32,321 --> 01:47:34,718
Baby! Baby!

1703
01:47:34,719 --> 01:47:38,368
Oh, baby. Baby.
Oh, baby. Oh! Baby!

1704
01:47:38,369 --> 01:47:40,924
Now? Oh, baby, baby,
baby! Baby now!

1705
01:47:40,925 --> 01:47:43,896
- Baby?
- Ray, it's time to go!

1706
01:47:44,209 --> 01:47:46,294
- Baby. Come on.
- You got'em?

1707
01:47:46,711 --> 01:47:49,839
Hey, you take visa? Take it!

1708
01:47:51,196 --> 01:47:54,845
What were you thinking tonight,
watching them go through...

1709
01:47:55,367 --> 01:47:58,285
The entire human
emotional experience?

1710
01:47:58,286 --> 01:48:01,937
