he doesn't get injured."

1711
01:48:03,292 --> 01:48:05,378
I felt responsible.

1712
01:48:07,255 --> 01:48:11,948
Sometimes I can't tell at all what's
going on in that head of yours.

1713
01:48:15,389 --> 01:48:17,266
Uhhhh...

1714
01:48:17,267 --> 01:48:20,395
And I really don't
know your noises yet.

1715
01:48:21,750 --> 01:48:24,252
Well, when you
wonder, ask me.

1716
01:48:24,253 --> 01:48:26,965
Okay, I will.

1717
01:48:28,842 --> 01:48:31,449
I thought I just did.

1718
01:48:34,889 --> 01:48:38,019
Why do you love me?
Why do you love me?

1719
01:48:40,313 --> 01:48:42,242
Can I come in and watch TV?

1720
01:48:42,243 --> 01:48:45,319
In a minute, sweetheart.
Just for a few minutes.

1721
01:49:04,819 --> 01:49:07,947
Hang in there, okay?
He's not going anywhere.

1722
01:49:07,948 --> 01:49:12,015
I know. Could we talk
about something else?

1723
01:49:12,328 --> 01:49:15,456
I don't think so. I'm
incapable of small talk.

1724
01:49:15,457 --> 01:49:19,001
But that's
why you love me, right?

1725
01:49:30,890 --> 01:49:34,434
I want you to know I'm
about personal attention.

1726
01:49:34,435 --> 01:49:38,032
This is my life. I'm available
to you 24 hours a day.

1727
01:49:38,034 --> 01:49:40,432
I'm in my office.
Call me anytime.

1728
01:49:40,433 --> 01:49:44,133
I'll be in Phoenix tomorrow for monday
night football. I can be in Indiana...

1729
01:49:44,134 --> 01:49:46,426
By 11:30 tuesday morning.

1730
01:49:46,427 --> 01:49:50,807
Just give me 20 minutes. I'm
not asking for an answer now.

1731
01:49:50,808 --> 01:49:53,413
Why don't you...
I'll call you tomorrow.

1732
01:49:53,414 --> 01:49:56,438
Just enjoy the rest of your day. Tell
Douglas I said hello, would you, please?

1733
01:49:56,439 --> 01:49:59,984
All right. Thank you. Same
to you, Marilee. Bye-bye.

1734
01:50:02,800 --> 01:50:04,987
Indiana, tuesday.

1735
01:50:04,989 --> 01:50:08,119
I'll be there.

1736
01:50:10,413 --> 01:50:12,498
It's my fault.

1737
01:50:13,958 --> 01:50:15,939
What?

1738
01:50:15,940 --> 01:50:20,006
It's not fair to you,
this whole thing.

1739
01:50:23,343 --> 01:50:27,098
Here. Tell me.

1740
01:50:27,411 --> 01:50:30,955
Let me help.
I took advantage of you.

1741
01:50:30,956 --> 01:50:35,128
The worst of it is that I'm not alone.
I did this with a kid.

1742
01:50:36,483 --> 01:50:39,611
I was just...
On some wild ride...

1743
01:50:39,924 --> 01:50:43,575
Where I thought that I was in love...
Enough...

1744
01:50:43,992 --> 01:50:47,432
For both of us.

1745
01:50:47,433 --> 01:50:50,561
I pretended that proposal
by the car was real,

1746
01:50:50,562 --> 01:50:53,586
And it might've just
been a hypothetical.

1747
01:50:55,984 --> 01:50:58,485
I did this,

1748
01:50:58,486 --> 01:51:02,449
And at least I can do
something about it now.

1749
01:51:02,450 --> 01:51:05,473
I'm not a guy who runs.

1750
01:51:05,474 --> 01:51:08,080
I stick.

1751
01:51:09,436 --> 01:51:11,938
Well, I don't need you to stick.

1752
01:51:11,939 --> 01:51:14,545
What do you want?
I don't know.

1753
01:51:14,546 --> 01:51:16,526
My soul or something?

1754
01:51:16,527 --> 01:51:19,031
Why not? I deserve that.

1755
01:51:19,969 --> 01:51:22,575
What if I'm not built that way?

1756
01:51:22,576 --> 01:51:25,495
I think we made a mistake.

1757
01:51:25,496 --> 01:51:28,625
No, no. Listen.
What if it's true? It's...

1758
01:51:30,397 --> 01:51:33,420
Great at friendship,
bad at intimacy.

1759
01:51:33,421 --> 01:51:38,531
I mean, come on, it's the theme...
of my bachelor film, for God's sake.

1760
01:51:38,532 --> 01:51:40,929
I know. I watched it.

1761
01:51:40,930 --> 01:51:43,536
I sort of... Know it by heart.

1762
01:51:46,457 --> 01:51:49,063
I don't like to give up.

1763
01:51:49,064 --> 01:51:51,565
Please, Jerry.

1764
01:51:51,566 --> 01:51:54,173
My need to make the
best of things...

1765
01:51:54,174 --> 01:51:57,093
And your need
to be responsible.

1766
01:51:57,094 --> 01:52:00,117
If one of us doesn't say
something about it now,

1767
01:52:00,119 --> 01:52:03,141
We could lose
ten years being polite.

1768
01:52:06,062 --> 01:52:10,233
Let's just call this next
road trip what it really is:

1769
01:52:11,484 --> 01:52:13,779
A nice, long break.

1770
01:52:21,495 --> 01:52:23,686
What about Ray?

1771
01:52:27,648 --> 01:52:30,046
Well, you'll be friends.

1772
01:52:31,924 --> 01:52:34,635
Friends?
Friends.

1773
01:52:37,972 --> 01:52:40,056
Of course you'll be friends.

1774
01:52:40,057 --> 01:52:42,769
I'll take him to the zoo.

1775
01:52:47,044 --> 01:52:50,068
So this break is a breakup.
That's...

1776
01:52:50,069 --> 01:52:53,719
Come on, Jerry. You know
this isn't easy for me.

1777
01:52:55,596 --> 01:52:59,141
On the surface
everything looks fine.

1778
01:52:59,142 --> 01:53:01,123
I've got this great guy,

1779
01:53:03,104 --> 01:53:05,607
And he loves my kid,

1780
01:53:08,110 --> 01:53:11,760
And he sure does like me a lot.

1781
01:53:17,600 --> 01:53:20,728
And I can't live like that.

1782
01:53:22,918 --> 01:53:25,629
It's not how I'm built.

1783
01:53:28,653 --> 01:53:32,303
<i>♪ She's got a secret garden</i>

1784
01:53:33,033 --> 01:53:36,266
<i>♪ Where everything you want</i>

1785
01:53:39,081 --> 01:53:42,835
<i>♪ Where everything you need</i>

1786
01:53:44,609 --> 01:53:47,632
<i>♪ will always stay</i>

1787
01:53:47,633 --> 01:53:50,656
<i>♪ a million</i>

1788
01:53:50,657 --> 01:53:55,975
<i>♪ miles away ♪♪</i>

1789
01:53:58,686 --> 01:54:01,293
If this is empty,

1790
01:54:01,606 --> 01:54:04,214
This doesn't matter.

1791
01:54:25,278 --> 01:54:27,781
It was just a
mission statement.

1792
01:54:43,632 --> 01:54:46,343
Put your arms out.
Let's see.

1793
01:54:46,344 --> 01:54:49,368
All right, let's see
what you've got here.

1794
01:55:00,630 --> 01:55:04,801
Hey, Rod, buddy, dude. I was wondering
